{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act12side", "eventName": "多索雷斯假日", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "DH-5", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "曲徑求勝", "storyInfo": "陳林二人一走進武器店，店內就發生了爆炸，引得觀眾席和主持台驚呼。\n廢墟中，兩人冷靜討論後，解除危機。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "largebg", "attributes": {"imagegroup": "bg_20_G04_1/bg_20_G04_2", "solidwidth": "920/920", "solidheight": 720.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_NPC_017_3"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$chasing_intro", "key": "$chasing_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼辦，鼠膽龍威隊遭到了官方設置的伏兵的圍堵。", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "混戰之中，埃內斯托小弟選擇了殿後，而接過他鑰匙的兩位女俠則繼續向前。", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃內斯托小弟雖然戰鬥力同樣不俗，但是敵人如此眾多，落敗也只是時間問題！", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而反觀兩位女俠這邊，雖然突破了包圍圈，但是前方依然有伏兵，她們真的能夠順利逃脫嗎？", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦？她們打開了路邊一家店的門然後衝了進去！", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這家店......", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#1"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是埃內斯托開的店。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_NPC_017_3"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原來如此，看來埃內斯托小弟丟給兩位女俠的鑰匙就是讓她們躲入自己的店中。", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，這樣真的有效嗎？", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，導播，切一下鏡頭！", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原來如此，從另一角度看過去就明白了，這家店是有後門的。", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而我們可以看到，後門有一條直通大道的小路，而這條路還沒有被其他阻攔者發現！", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這會是鼠膽龍威隊的機會嗎，還是——", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_explo_n"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "D.D.D.的話音未落，螢幕中，埃內斯托的武器店就發出巨大的爆炸聲。"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_NPC_017_3"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這、這這這究竟是什麼情況？", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "坎黛拉女士，這也是您設置的障礙嗎？", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#2"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果我要設置，那就不是只炸這一家店這麼簡單了。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#2"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_NPC_017_3"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這......難道是其他隊伍知道埃內斯托小弟有這樣的後手而設下的陷阱？！", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果是這樣，那鼠膽龍威隊這一次可以說是被徹底算計了！", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鼠膽龍威隊，難道要折戟於此了嗎！", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_190_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好過分......陳小姐和林小姐不會有事吧？", "name": "艾雅法拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_190_1#2"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_190_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放心，她們兩個都是老江湖，這點爆炸死不了。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_190_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_203_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只不過嘛......雖然這種比賽耍手段不奇怪，但這也有點太針對了。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#5"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老陳這是和誰結梁子了嗎。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#5"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "largebg", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_20_G02"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_194"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......嘖，這傢伙，怎麼回事，根本打不著他。", "name": "伏兵A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_437_mizuki_1#4"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咦......那邊好像是陳姐姐她們去的方向。", "name": "水月"}, "figure_art": "avg_437_mizuki_1#4"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_437_mizuki_1#1"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是過去看一看吧。", "name": "水月"}, "figure_art": "avg_437_mizuki_1#1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "dialog", 